title: Cinderella - Theme for Beauty, Hair and Spa - WordPress
description:
Cinderella | WordPress Theme for Beauty, Hair and SPA Salons is the product which has been made especially for Small Businesses in Beauty Industry. It has the capacity to equally fit a Single Local Salon as well as a Network of Salons with Multiple Locations. Contains external links.

To install:

1. Upload to the plugin folder in wordpress
2. Activate through the plugin menu in wp-admin
